Product Version     25.10    Cadence Design Systems, Inc.
timing_constr..._clock_latency(25.10)    timing_constr..._clock_latency(25.10)

Name
       timing_constraint_path_delay_exclude_io_delay_from_ignore_clock_latency

Syntax
       timing_constraint_path_delay_exclude_io_delay_from_ignore_clock_latency
       {true | false}

       Default: false

       Excludes the input/output delays from slack computation.

       When  set  to  true, the software excludes the input/output delays from
       slack  computation   for   paths   constrained   by   the   set_max_de-
       lay/set_min_delay -ignore_clock_latency command.

       To set this global variable, use the set command.

